text.section:
Labeling for a food product or food containing or consisting of surimi shall include 1 or more of the following terms, as appropriate:
"Imitation crab";
"Imitation lobster";
"Imitation scallops";
"Imitation shrimp";
"Imitation" followed by the name of the seafood imitated;
"Artificial processed seafood";
"Surimi";
"Seafood salad containing imitation" followed by the name of the seafood imitated; or
Other terms approved by the Department.
